very conspicuous. It has been done, yes. Certain children are liked better than other\rquote s which of course is natural if they - if the child is nice the teachers turn - are going to be nice.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9647720 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14944549\charrsid5711483 Were there any gangs or groups in your school.
