Left out of things. No, I don't think so. I think most of the children in my school were treated pretty well the same as each other. Wasn't a lot of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9647720 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14944549\charrsid5711483 Amongst themselves?
