Yes, I wouldn't have left when I did. 'Course maybe mother wanted me away to earn a bit of money, I don't know, she - probably that but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9647720 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14944549\charrsid5711483 You didn't mind?
